OL,3,CBritish man in 'critical but stable
OL,4,Ccondition' after Tobago shark attack
OL,6,FThe man sustained injuries to his left
OL,7,Fhand, left thigh, and stomach
OL,8,Ffollowing the attack on Friday, ITV
OL,9,FNews' Natasha Potts reports
OL,11,FA British tourist is in intensive care
OL,12,Fon the Caribbean island of Tobago
OL,13,Fafter being seriously injured in a
OL,14,Fshark attack.
OL,16,FThe man, identified by local officials
OL,17,Fas a 64-year-old Peter Smith, from
OL,18,FHertfordshire, was attacked 10 metres
OL,19,Foff the shore near the Starfish Hotel
OL,20,Fin Courland Bay, on the north coast.
