OL,3,CBritish man in 'critical but stable
OL,4,Ccondition' after Tobago shark attack
OL,6,FHe is said to be in a "critical but
OL,7,Fstable" condition with injuries to his
OL,8,Fleft hand, left thigh, and stomach
OL,9,Ffollowing the attack on Friday morning.
OL,11,FHis attacker was a bull shark
OL,12,Festimated to be eight to 10 ft long
OL,13,Fand 2 ft wide, the Tobago House of
OL,14,FAssembly said.
OL,16,FA 10,000 US dollar (#1,179) bounty
OL,17,Fpreviously offered by authorities to
OL,18,Fanyone who could capture the shark was
OL,19,Flater retracted.
