OL,6,FHe said Mr Smith had been holidaying
OL,7,Fon the island with his wife and
OL,8,Ffriends and had been due to fly home
OL,9,Fthat day.
OL,11,FChief Secretary Farley Augustine said
OL,12,Fin a Facebook press briefing on Friday
OL,13,Fevening that the man had been
OL,14,Fholidaying on the island with his wife
OL,15,Fand friends and had been due to fly
OL,16,Fhome that day.
