OL,3,CBritish man in 'critical but stable
OL,4,Ccondition' after Tobago shark attack
OL,6,FMr Augustine said the man was stable
OL,7,Fand "doing well", but remained in an
OL,8,Fintensive care unit and kept under
OL,9,Fsedation at Scarborough General
OL,10,FHospital.
OL,12,FHe went on: "Some reattachments were
OL,13,Fdone, of fingers for example, and
OL,14,Fhopefully that will save those fingers.
OL,16,F"We know that there's significant
OL,17,Fwounds on one of his legs that cannot
OL,18,Fbe completely closed, but he will
OL,19,Frequire extensive work.
