OL,6,F"The task at this time for our health
OL,7,Fprofessionals is really to stabilise
OL,8,Fand ensure that we can save life and
OL,9,Flimb as much as possible."
OL,11,FMr Augustine added that the local
OL,12,Fgovernment was working closely with
OL,13,Fthe British High Commission. Several
OL,14,Fbeaches and coastal areas were closed
OL,15,Fas a precaution.
OL,17,FLast year, there were 69 unprovoked
OL,18,Fattacks and 22 provoked bites
OL,19,Fworldwide, along with 14 fatalities,
OL,20,Faccording to the Florida-based
OL,21,FInternational Shark Attack File.
